== Three versions ==

* {{color|blue|text=Blue = Easy}}
* {{color|yellow|text=Yellow = Normal}}
* {{color|purple|text=Purple = Legendary}}

All three versions use the same storyline about the testing-process that the entity (named [[Enemy-Equilibrium|Equilibrium]]) performs on the [[Federation]] crew, a [[Romulan]] crew, and a [[Klingon]] crew ; {{EventText02|12|7}} 

