=== Scoring ===
concerning points: the Mission-points listed below are the max-amount of points possible per-win...
====Trivia====
* the chart below has the normally-correct autocalculated values of 25/50/75-points per win (increasing per level).
* however, the points for level 11.5 '''but ''' '''''ONLY''''' ''' that level''' were accidentally-repeated from level 11,  thus that row (and combined totals) are actually off by 25/50/75-points from their correct-values due to this bug.  again, the level 12 points fell back into line with their correct (autocalculated) values...
* the Mission-points listed are the max-amount of points possible per-win which gets reset (per win) after an elapsed wall-clock time of 1 hour...  if you decide to play the same-level (after winning) immediately, the points are cut in half...  the actual-points per win are always listed at the first-screen of a level.  so, if you are unsure if an hour has elapsed since the last time you won a level, just check the screen for the number of points (it will list a timer till the next reset, if needed)...

