=== Scoring ===
Scoring details (maximum) per mission...
For a description of the scoring-chart, see: [[Events in general#Scoring]]
==== Trivia ====
* For this first-pass several issues seem to be present...
** The Bonus-levels are activating one-level-early compared to the graphic...  For instance, the graphic shows lvl-1, lvl-2, then bonus-lvl-2.5 next to lvl-2...  However, the levels are opening in the order lvl-1, lvl-2.5, and then lvl-2...
** The scoring for the levels is very inconsistent with normal increases...  For instance, the usual increase for the same-first-levels should be 25 points per level...  However, the first-bonus-level-2.5 gave the unusually-high value of 225 points..
* Thankfully, the scoring-ratios across series seems to have stayed consistent...  So if the Easy levels are value-X, then the Normal levels are valued twice-as-high...  (and Legendary-levels have values of three-X)...
** Current scores (vs. expected-charting) is as follows:
** 25 (25), 50 (50), b-225 (b-75), 
** 25 (100), 175 (125), 100 (150), b-300 (b-175), 
** 350 (200), b-375 (b-225), 
** 200 (250), 250 (275), 350 (300), b-425 (b-325),
** 275 (350), 400 (375), 275 (400), b-425 (b-425),
** 225 (450), 150 (475)
* At current-scoring-amounts, one full set (hard) gives 13,350+450=13.8k overall giving 55.2k (hard) for all-4-sets...  so 18.4k easy and 36.8k medium...
